1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:41,719
Your Highness,

3
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,039
the Prince has returned.

4
00:00:44,479 --> 00:00:45,920
You should be happy.

5
00:00:46,439 --> 00:00:48,159
Should I be happy?

6
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:52,079
The Prince is back.

7
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:54,479
I dressed so carefully,

8
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:57,079
yet he still went to her.

9
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:58,240
Your Highness,

10
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:03,079
your plan was to bring the Prince back

11
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,640
and keep him here.

12
00:01:05,319 --> 00:01:06,599
That may be true,

13
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:10,280
but I'm still unhappy.

14
00:01:11,140 --> 00:01:14,980
=Episode 22=

15
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,439
Like a lotus rising from clear water,

16
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,439
naturally beautiful without
decoration.

17
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:31,480
Do you know my favorite is
the light and plain,

18
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,040
like orchids?

19
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,840
Your Highness, I don't understand.

20
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:40,280
I meant I'm interested in you.

21
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:50,159
We haven't done the marriage rites.

22
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,879
It would be improper.

23
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,159
I wouldn't dare.

24
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,200
Are you afraid?

25
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,640
Or unwilling?

26
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,719
I'm already here.

27
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:01,239
Do you still need to ask?

28
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,519
If you are so inclined,

29
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:05,200
then on this full moon night,

30
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:07,319
give yourself to me.

31
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,240
My Lady!

32
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,199
My Lady!

33
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,240
So here you are.

34
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,120
I searched everywhere.

35
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,599
I finally found you.

36
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:25,520
Xiaotao said you'd drink a lot tonight.

37
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,840
She made you hangover soup.

38
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,319
Perfect.

39
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:33,080
I do have a bit of a headache.

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,680
Drinking really clouds the mind.

41
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,280
What a waste of this full moon.

42
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,159
Go on.

43
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,319
Miss Rulan,

44
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,639
are you alright?

45
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,360
Don't worry. I met the Prince today.

46
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:07,800
He seems straightforward,

47
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,639
nothing inappropriate.

48
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,520
Li Xiaoshou succeeded at
Yanyu Embroidery House.

49
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,240
Wu Lian embroidered the victims' names

50
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,840
onto handkerchief.

51
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,960
Ironclad evidence.

52
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,159
We can act now.

53
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,599
Wait.

54
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,199
One more thing.

55
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,400
His crimes are clear.

56
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,439
What else is missing?

57
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,879
We need an embroiderer willing
to testify.

58
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,639
Testify?

59
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,240
That's not easy.

60
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,199
But the Flower Festival is almost here.

61
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,280
If we miss it,

62
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,479
we may never get another
chance like this.

63
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,479
It's fine.

64
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,479
I've made arrangements.

65
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,759
I'm just worried about Miss Rulan...

66
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,000
I need one more thing too.

67
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,479
Mr. Liu,

68
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,680
Everything at the Flower Festival
hinges on this.

69
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,479
Your Highness,

70
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,479
Lady Cheng'en requests an audience.

71
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,039
You may enter.

72
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,680
You're not with the Prince?

73
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,759
Yet you come to see me.

74
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,639
I belong to you.

75
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:21,399
Of course I come to you first.

76
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,160
What is it?

77
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,519
After talking with the Prince today,

78
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:29,800
I discovered someone in
this manor

79
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:31,759
wants to harm you.

80
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,560
Who would wish to harm me?

81
00:04:34,879 --> 00:04:36,120
Wu Lian.

82
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:40,680
If you're just going to keep
fighting with him,

83
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,120
don't bother telling me.

84
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,759
Wu Lian knows my taste perfectly.

85
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:46,279
In all of Jinxiu City,

86
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,639
only he can embroider
what I want.

87
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:52,959
Your Highness,

88
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:56,879
Master Wu has brought the
Flower Festival gown.

89
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,519
Please try on the gown, Your Highness.

90
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,279
Ask him in...

91
00:04:59,279 --> 00:04:59,800
Wenyue,

92
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,920
If you care to hear my words,

93
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,160
I'll continue.

94
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,519
But if you prefer

95
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:06,360
to have Wu Lian help you
try on the gown,

96
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,439
then I'll take my leave.

97
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,360
Luoxia,

98
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,959
tell him to go back and rest early.

99
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:13,120
Yes.

100
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,240
Speak.

101
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,279
The Prince has been away for years.

102
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,319
He is no stranger to luxury.

103
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,439
But when he returned,

104
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,959
he only saw plain and light clothes.

105
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,720
Wu Lian's embroidery is excellent,

106
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:32,600
but he always uses light colors
for your gowns.

107
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,519
Now that the Prince is back,

108
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,319
seeing you dressed and acting

109
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,040
as elegantly as ever,

110
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:40,160
it may lack novelty.

111
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,800
Go on.

112
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:51,759
The camellia comes from a foreign land.

113
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,639
Beautiful as it is,

114
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:56,199
at the Flower Festival ceremony,

115
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:59,439
if someone claims you have ties
with foreign lands,

116
00:05:59,879 --> 00:06:00,959
how will you explain?

117
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,519
He's just a craftsman.

118
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,040
What does he know of foreign matters?

119
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,360
An ordinary man might not know.

120
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:11,399
But Wu Lian is a master
in the embroidery world.

121
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,120
In Jinxiu City,

122
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,680
his associates are rich and powerful.

123
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,959
He would have heard.

124
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,040
The Prince went on a campaign
to pacify the foreign lands.

125
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:22,959
If he meant no harm,

126
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:25,279
why would he embroider this?

127
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,920
He dares to harbor such thoughts.

128
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,879
Master Wu,

129
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:39,879
Her Highness asks you
not to wait any longer.

130
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:43,040
Lady Cheng'en is discussing gowns
with her inside.

131
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,600
Does she like it?

132
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:49,399
Lady Cheng'en says you only know
elaborate designs

133
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,839
to please Her Highness,

134
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,920
but they don't suit His Highness's taste.

135
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:55,439
Perhaps you did it on purpose.

136
00:06:56,319 --> 00:07:00,600
And the camellias
are from foreign lands.

137
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,120
What did Her Highness say?

138
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:05,879
Forget it.

139
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:13,680
Still no witnesses today.

140
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:16,240
I talked to those ladies,

141
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:18,639
but whenever Yanyu Embroidery
House comes up,

142
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,439
they clam up.

143
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:29,000
This last step is hard and risky.

144
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:32,319
If those girls won't testify,

145
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:34,560
the handkerchief and needles

146
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:37,360
would have died with Ms. Meng Wan.

147
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,040
Continue the search tomorrow.

148
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:43,199
How did it go?

149
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,279
After hearing my words,

150
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,480
she won't see Wu Lian anymore.

151
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,319
Without the Princess Consort as
his shield,

152
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,079
Wu Lian will never recover.

153
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,160
Xiaojiu, go and find Mr. Liu.

154
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,199
Tell them this is the final step.

155
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:56,920
We got it.

156
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,639
Yes.

157
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,439
Wu Lian of Yanyu Embroidery House

158
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,240
requests an audience
with Your Highness.

159
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,920
So you're the embroiderer
my wife favors most.

160
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,040
Yes.

161
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,680
What brings you here?

162
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,160
Your Highness,

163
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,360
I have something to say.

164
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:25,680
The Lady Cheng'en currently in the manor

165
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:28,319
is an impostor.

166
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,519
Are you aware of your crime?

167
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,840
I am.

168
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:36,200
I know speaking against a superior
is a grave offense.

169
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:39,039
But knowing the truth
and hiding it is worse.

170
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:42,559
I stake the reputation of
Yanyu Embroidery House

171
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,799
that every word I say is true.

172
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,159
If not,

173
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:48,039
I submit to your punishment.

174
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,200
Speak.

175
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,440
The current Lady Cheng'en

176
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:55,799
is an embroiderer from my house
in disguise.

177
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:58,960
Years ago, she fell for me.
I rejected her.

178
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:00,200
Three years ago,

179
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:02,559
she jumped from the city wall.

180
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:03,840
Continue.

181
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:07,879
I fear this woman will bring
disaster to Jinxiu City.

182
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:14,159
Nanny Du, I had nightmares all night.

183
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,440
You're carrying too much worry.

184
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:19,039
I'll have them make a calming tea.

185
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:24,559
Where did the Prince stay last night?

186
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:27,000
He never left the study.

187
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,440
But...

188
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,360
But what?

189
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,399
Don't hide it.

190
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:37,240
Master Wu went to the study
early this morning.

191
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:40,399
He spoke with the Prince
for a long time.

192
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:46,759
Is Wu Lian truly trying
to harm me?

193
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,519
I have seen Master Wu's loyalty

194
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,759
to you with my own eyes.

195
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,080
But

196
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,919
there are rumors among the people

197
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,240
that Wu Lian bullies others

198
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,799
and controls the manor.

199
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,559
A false lady

200
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:06,879
has exposed a true villain.

201
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,759
Get my change of clothes ready.

202
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,320
Yes.

203
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,080
If what you say is true...

204
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,000
Her Highness arrives!

205
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:28,840
Your Highness,

206
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:32,039
it's been years since you
tasted my cooking.

207
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,799
Don't you want to hear his words?

208
00:10:39,679 --> 00:10:42,720
How dare you speak out
of turn before the Prince?

209
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,519
I've tolerated you like a dog
following me,

210
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:47,440
sparing your dignity.

211
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:50,840
Yet you dared to embroider
foreign flowers

212
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,600
on my Flower Festival gown.

213
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:55,320
Do you want to humiliate me
before the entire city?

214
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,399
No, no, no!

215
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,120
Your Highness,

216
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,000
I truly didn't know.

217
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,639
I only thought the flowers
were very vibrant.

218
00:11:01,639 --> 00:11:02,399
How dare you!

219
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,440
You mingle with the rich
and powerful.

220
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:05,679
How could you not know?

221
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,600
Guards!

222
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,200
Confine Wu Lian to his house.

223
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,320
He may not leave.

224
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:12,279
Your Highness!

225
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,120
Your Highness!

226
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:22,879
It's been three years.

227
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:25,000
You have no idea

228
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,440
what I've done to bring you back.

229
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:27,960
Now that I've seen you,

230
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:30,000
I wish I hadn't.

231
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,679
Is lawlessness part of your plan?

232
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,960
Have you investigated?

233
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:11,620
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

234
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:14,860
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

235
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,820
♪The past no longer binds♪

236
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:23,020
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

237
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:27,580
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

238
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:31,300
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

239
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:33,660
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

240
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:37,740
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

241
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:40,340
♪For your faith that never broke♪

242
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:44,660
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

243
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:47,460
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

244
00:12:47,460 --> 00:12:51,700
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

245
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:55,380
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

246
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:58,140
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

247
00:12:58,140 --> 00:13:00,740
♪One thought turns into ash♪

248
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:07,060
♪No future left to write♪

249
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:09,940
♪If I never fall♪

250
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:12,340
♪How could this waiting end♪

251
00:13:12,340 --> 00:13:13,700
♪If I bear no scars♪

252
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:16,020
♪How could I challenge fate♪

253
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:18,380
♪I knew there was no way back♪

254
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:22,380
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

255
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,620
♪For your faith that never broke♪

256
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:28,780
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

257
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,660
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

258
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:36,060
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

259
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:39,740
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

260
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:42,340
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

261
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,700
♪One thought turns into ash♪

262
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:51,060
♪No future left to write♪

263
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:54,340
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

264
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:57,740
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

265
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:01,620
♪If we meet again someday♪

266
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:07,860
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪

